Package transbit.tbits.report

Class Summary
CustomReport This servlet is used to generate custom reports
GetAuditInfo This servlet is used to return the status,lastupdated and updated time of a particular request or all requests in that business area
GroupedRequestSummary This class generates a summary of requests attended during a given period.
MailDailyRequestsWorkedOn The MailDailyRequestsWorkedOn class generates reports listing all tasks worked on today or a specified period for the specified business area
MailListOfUnclosedTasks The MailDailyOfUnclosedTasks class generates reports listing all unclosed tasks.
PerUserReportEmailer This class executes and emails report to every active user selected.
It consumes certain params and spits out remaining (plus some more) params to the report.
TBitsReportEngine This is a Singleton class which wraps the BirtReportEngine and provide developer-friendly methods to create the reports.
TBitsReportMailer
